{"tid":567100,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"【海洋生物】淺談水母","createTime":"2018-02-20T14:16:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-27T14:20:06.000Z","uid":132565,"like":273,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":79,"replies":[{"pid":"6518348d3962e2e715d3da4838533fbb07b4af4c","tid":567100,"uid":132565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T14:16:48.000Z","msg":"大家好又係我呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 新年祝大家心想事成身體健康<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n今次又黎同大家講下水母呢種奇妙，神秘，但又好簡單既生物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://www.natgeokids.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/jellyfish-facts-2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.natgeokids.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F02%2Fjellyfish-facts-2.jpg&h=f2a11c79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://finedininglovers.cdn.crosscast-system.com/BlogPost/xl_11832_jellyfish-finedininglovers-tp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffinedininglovers.cdn.crosscast-system.com%2FBlogPost%2Fxl_11832_jellyfish-finedininglovers-tp.jpg&h=088318d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n水母係屬於<span style=\"color: orange;\">刺胞動物門(Cnidaria)</span>，呢個門可以分成4大group: <span style=\"color: blue;\">水母</span>，<span style=\"color: teal;\">箱水母</span>，<span style=\"color: purple;\">海葵<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">同佢啲朋友</span></span>，<span style=\"color: purple;\">水螅</span>。我會講前兩者，後兩者因為較冷門有人想知再講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">生命循環</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.pinimg.com/736x/74/87/83/74878326e9db84e3dbf75655f6b4b045--life-cycles-jellyfish.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.pinimg.com%2F736x%2F74%2F87%2F83%2F74878326e9db84e3dbf75655f6b4b045--life-cycles-jellyfish.jpg&h=539b2990&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n同好多無脊椎動物相似，水母有一個<span style=\"color: green;\">完全變態既生命循環</span>。首先，係海水中浮游既<span style=\"color: navy;\">精同卵結合</span>，長大成一隻<span style=\"color: purple;\">浮游生物(Swimming planula)</span>。佢會浮歷大海，嘗試搵地方發展。搵到岩心水既位置佢就會定落黎，變成一個叫<span style=\"color: violet;\">Polyp</span>既野。當呢個Polyp長大，佢會開始進行無性繁殖，生產大量<span style=\"color: orange;\">馬杜莎(Medusa)</span>。而呢啲<span style=\"color: orange;\">馬杜莎(Medusa)</span>，就係我地常見到既水母。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">結構</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"http://cronodon.com/images/aurelia-3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcronodon.com%2Fimages%2Faurelia-3.jpg&h=730bbd59&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><ins>馬杜莎階段既水母</ins></span>，有好簡單既生理結構。中間Mesogloea係一層啫喱，由<span style=\"color: green;\">表層Epidermis</span>同<span style=\"color: purple;\">內面Gastrodermis</span>一層薄細胞層包住，所以佢地好水，好有彈性。當中有<span style=\"color: brown;\">肌肉環</span>，所以佢地只可以做簡單既收縮運動，&quot;唧&quot;水推進身體。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">刺細胞(Cnidocyte)</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://projects.ncsu.edu/project/bio402_315/new%20cnidaria/cnidocyte.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fprojects.ncsu.edu%2Fproject%2Fbio402_315%2Fnew%2520cnidaria%2Fcnidocyte.gif&h=9d5e8a9c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.stingaway.co/communities/4/004/013/230/884//images/4624667341.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.stingaway.co%2Fcommunities%2F4%2F004%2F013%2F230%2F884%2F%2Fimages%2F4624667341.gif&h=37a768e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n刺細胞通常係水母既觸手上搵到。擁有<span style=\"color: violet;\">刺細胞</span>係<ins>刺胞動物門</ins>入面既其中一個特點，呢啲刺細胞有分幾種，大部份都係好似上圖咁，會<span style=\"color: red;\">刺穿皮膚入肉再放毒素</span>，有啲只會痴住獵物，仲有啲直情唔係用黎獵食。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">講完大路野，就個別再講下我覺得得意既水母啦</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">箱水母(Box Jellyfish)</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://images.huffingtonpost.com/2013-07-04-boxangel1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.huffingtonpost.com%2F2013-07-04-boxangel1.jpg&h=a109a466&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.aquarium.co.za/cache/ce_img_cache/local/24be6a810f238a37/box_jelly_900_600_70.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aquarium.co.za%2Fcache%2Fce_img_cache%2Flocal%2F24be6a810f238a37%2Fbox_jelly_900_600_70.jpg&h=b0f8d617&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n比傳統水母<span style=\"color: red;\">更快，更毒，更&quot;有腦&quot;</span>。佢地外表上<ins>好似一個鐘(Bell)</ins>咁，係下面既觸手唔似傳統水母咁分佈，而係集中係四角。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">葡萄牙戰艦(Portuguese man o' war)</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.images.dailystar.co.uk/dynamic/1/photos/267000/620x/portuguese-man-of-war-jellyfish-invasion-britian-649600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.images.dailystar.co.uk%2Fdynamic%2F1%2Fphotos%2F267000%2F620x%2Fportuguese-man-of-war-jellyfish-invasion-britian-649600.jpg&h=f2eaaf41&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/CzcTcs9UkAABPkM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FCzcTcs9UkAABPkM.jpg&h=15e07585&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n佢地<span style=\"color: red;\">非常毒</span>，而且唔太算係水母，起碼唔係普通馬杜莎式水母。因為一隻葡萄牙戰艦<span style=\"color: orange;\">係一個水螅社群</span>，意思就係一隻戰艦，由好多隻水螅組成。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">永生水母(Immortal Jellyfish)</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://spydersden.files.wordpress.com/2013/05/jellyfish.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fspydersden.files.wordpress.com%2F2013%2F05%2Fjellyfish.jpg&h=f92af336&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.abc.net.au/radionational/image/7666334-3x2-700x467.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.abc.net.au%2Fradionational%2Fimage%2F7666334-3x2-700x467.jpg&h=def5af8f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢種水母有<span style=\"color: orange;\">還原成Polyp既能力</span>，佢既細胞可以改變成第二種細胞，因而可以還原再生。理論上佢地可以永生，因為佢地一有事就可以還原再刷。實質上都係會比其他生物食／其他環境因素而死。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">不過一講水母，就通常會有啲誤會，為免大家係心儀對象面前拋錯書包，請留意以下兩點</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">第一，海天使(Sea Angel)唔係水母黎</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/3N5_ShK6OOY/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2F3N5_ShK6OOY%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=c1b2dd89&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/tDVrTrS.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FtDVrTrS.gif&h=bd298439&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n佢地係海蛞蝓，同水母係無關係。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">第二，男/女神比水母炸親要點做?</span></span><br />\n有醋淋醋，因為<span style=\"color: orange;\">醋會令上文提到既刺細胞失去作用</span>，係淋醋之前千祈唔好亂郁啲水母鬚，以免觸發更多刺細胞。<span style=\"color: violet;\">尿，其他體液或酸性液體例如檸茶</span>都係<ins>無証據話得</ins>既。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">食法</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://qph.fs.quoracdn.net/main-qimg-89ee0c1fc70791fd087b0328f0eaaabc-c\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fqph.fs.quoracdn.net%2Fmain-qimg-89ee0c1fc70791fd087b0328f0eaaabc-c&h=2cf38880&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n廣東人做水母有好多種做法，水母本身無味，而且勁水同有毒，無可能新鮮食，所以都係做番海蜇撈黎食算啦<br />\n<br />\n中意既可以睇埋我其他post，但啲圖可能已過期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n[海洋生物]淺談八爪魚/墨魚/魷魚<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/342416/page/14?ref=web\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/342416/page/14?ref=web</a><br />\n<br />\n[海洋生物(2)]淺談海星/海膽/海參<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/343951/page/5?ref=web\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/343951/page/5?ref=web</a><br />\n<br />\n【海洋生物】淺談鯊魚 (長篇大論)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/347746/page/6?ref=web\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/347746/page/6?ref=web</a><br />\n<br />\n【海洋生物】淺談蝦蟹<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/359042/page/9?ref=web\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/359042/page/9?ref=web</a><br />\n<br />\n【海洋生物】淺談魚類 (序:由頭開始)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/369314/page/1?ref=web\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/369314/page/1?ref=web</a><br />\n<br />\n【海洋生物】淺談海洋哺乳類<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/421631/page/1?ref=web\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/421631/page/1?ref=web</a>"},{"pid":"182f9d7211e77869717a9c38702bf1d9fb3ad5c6","tid":567100,"uid":47303,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T14:17:35.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"f7498da722f7cbf2d5d93d31bd501a7275366a26","tid":567100,"uid":132565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"182f9d7211e77869717a9c38702bf1d9fb3ad5c6","tid":567100,"uid":47303,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T14:17:35.000Z","msg":"留名"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T14:28:07.000Z","msg":"多謝支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c5b427b1c7e6eb5dd68480757f6a688b809f771","tid":567100,"uid":3037,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T14:37:28.000Z","msg":"睇到好肚餓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9b3214f4c82d2b8c54e7e3923499cfbbc744fe3","tid":567100,"uid":83371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime