8.000Z","msg":"我大學嗰水母專家講jelly fish 可以define as gelatinous zooplankton,所以其實sea angel, salps 同 ctenophore果啲廣義上都算喺水母，但係 ，true jelly就真係係cnidarian先算"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T05:22:04.000Z","msg":"水母/Jellyfish本身就係一個統稱，所以隻生物個型狀/生活方式似都已經可以話係。<br />\n不過我唔想咁亂，分番開好啲"},{"pid":"08a1518011edb4e12acbe3050b5f58bffd248fb7","tid":567100,"uid":132565,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"cc3b8e10dae8553cf78a54047ba8e0b826fc76ff","tid":567100,"uid":36026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T18:12:03.000Z","msg":"因為一隻葡萄牙戰艦係一個水螅社群，意思就係一隻戰艦，由好多隻水螅組成。<br />\n<br />\n姐係呢個唔係水母?只係一堆水蛭?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T05:30:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">水螅(Hydrozoan)</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://images.fineartamerica.com/images-medium-large/hydrozoan-colony-alexander-semenov.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.fineartamerica.com%2Fimages-medium-large%2Fhydrozoan-colony-alexander-semenov.jpg&h=3d5f6520&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://web.stanford.edu/group/seanet/images/plumularia580.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fweb.stanford.edu%2Fgroup%2Fseanet%2Fimages%2Fplumularia580.jpg&h=3feb7d37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n同一般水母唔同，佢地大部分都係會一群一群咁生活，例如上圖既&quot;草叢&quot;，已經有幾十隻水螅係度。<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">水螅既生命大部分時間係Polyp形式</span>，只有某部分水螅會有馬杜莎式態。就算有都有好細隻/好短時間。<br />\n葡萄牙戰艦就係一堆水螅既Polyp，特別之處係浮水面。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">水蛭</span>係另一回事黎。"},{"pid":"2136f149e744a76ca5ff7e03d314dd7d52deea9d","tid":567100,"uid":27049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T05:34:22.000Z","msg":"入嚟為咗睇點食法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27794373c0dfcd3bee6f47eac4c5b36c509a83a7","tid":567100,"uid":71814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T05:37:29.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"b7bd58d491093e4e7d4aa7254e7086e62d816c0b"